{{version030}}
{{flavour|Throws a ball of hot steam towards a targeted creature.}}

'''Steam Ball''' is a monster-only spell which launches balls of super hot [[steam]], dealing moderate steam damage. It also creates [[cloud#Steam|steam clouds]], dealing more damage and potentially blocking [[line of sight]]. Having [[steam resistance]] or [[fire resistance]] reduces the impact damage by 66%, and gives immunity to steam clouds' damage.

